{
  "stem": "22972.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father's regimental commanders, several of whom were shot by Hitler before it was all over, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] made it possible for us to take some money out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got a wonderful exchange of, for half a million mark, we got $7,000.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was enough to give us a start even though, when we came to America, my father got a job for $25 a week.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was then 55 years old, and he got a job for $25 a week carrying refrigerators and stoves up and down four flights of stairs, which was not easy.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The first year in America was tougher, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The first year in America was tougher than all the years in-- in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother and I never knew whether my father would come home or whether he would have committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was very, very tough on this very proud man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One of the things that-- that came to mind earlier was that my father-- you could not just take your money out of the bank.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, if you took more than 100 mark out of the bank, you had to account for what you bought with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father slowly, slowly, slowly saved a mark here, 10 mark there, 50 mark there, and he bought gold coins on the black market.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when he had enough gold, he took it on the black market to a basement somewhere, where a man had set up a smelt.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, come back in a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
